description:
The Consumer Assessment of Healthcare Providers and Systems (CAHPS) for MIPS Group Survey is comprised of 10 Summary Survey Measures (SSMs) and measures patient experience of care within a group practice. The NQF endorsement status and endorsement id (if applicable) for each SSM utilized in this measure are as follows:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         - Getting timely care, appointments, and information;
- How well providers Communicate;
- Patient's Rating of Provider;
- Access to Specialists;
- Health Promotion & Education;
- Shared Decision Making;
- Health Status/Functional Status;
- Courteous and Helpful Office Staff;
- Care Coordination; and
- Stewardship of Patient Resources
